These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, amber, azure, orange
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
4. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
7. the person who likes amber is somewhere between the person who likes light-blue and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the person who likes amber and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who likes azure and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | light-blue | amber | azure     | orange |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, horror, adventure, documentary
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching documentary movies and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
4. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | spy | horror | adventure      | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
City: venice, san-francisco, london, new-york
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
6. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person traveling to san-francisco and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | san-francisco    | london   | venice    | new-york  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, blueberry, peach, asparagus
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the person eating blueberry##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person eating asparagus and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | asparagus | peach | grapes  | blueberry |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

