.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, indonesian, mexican
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the argentine and the chinese##7
2. the chinese is not to the right of the mexican##8
3. the mexican is on the right of the indonesian##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the argentine##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the mexican have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | gardening | filmmaking | singing |
| Pet     | chinese     | indonesian     | mexican     | argentine    |

