.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, papaya, pepper, watermelon
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, pakistani, indonesian, turkish
1. the turkish is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
2. the person eating watermelon and the turkish have the same parity positions##9
3. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the pakistani and the turkish##7
6. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | pepper | broccoli   | papaya | watermelon |
| Transport   | indonesian   | pakistani | dutch    | turkish      |

