2. the accountant is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the architect##1
7. the architect is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
8. the person watching comedy movies and the chef have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching family movies and the engineer have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | accountant   | architect  | engineer  | chef |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | family | mystery | comedy      |

