.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, azure, black, red
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, r&b, soul
 1. the person who likes azure and the fan r&b have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who likes black is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
 3. the fan blues is somewhere between the person who likes azure and the person who likes amber##7
 4. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the person who likes black##5
 5. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan r&b is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
 7. the person who likes red and the fan jazz have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
 9. the fan soul is in an odd position##4
10. the person who likes red is not to the right of the fan blues##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | amber  | red | black  | azure |
| Music-Genre   | soul | r&b     | blues | jazz     |

