1. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk and the havana-smoker have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | oliveros | havana   | vegafina   | fonseca   |

