.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, juice, water
There 4 different types of food: lemon, pineapple, watermelon, mango
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the person eating mango is not to the right of the person eating watermelon##8
 4. the person eating pineapple is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating lemon is not the person drinking cola##6
 6. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking water and the person eating pineapple have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 9. the person drinking water is the person eating pineapple##1
10. the person drinking cola and the person eating pineapple have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice        | water   | coffee      |
| Hobby      | mango | watermelon | pineapple | lemon |

 